# AgToosa QA Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-qa` or any QA work, follow `Docs/AgToosa_QA.md` precisely.

## Key constraints

- Every Must-priority AC from the active spec must have a passing test.
- Coverage must meet or exceed the threshold in `Docs/Context/workflow.md`.
- Browser/device matrix from `Docs/Context/tech-stack.md` must be fully covered.
- Run the test suite 3× to detect flaky tests before reporting pass.
- Regression tests for bug fixes must follow the naming pattern `regression_[bug-id]_*`.
